---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility for Dentists UK | Rank4AI" description="Get your dental practice recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini and Perplexity. AI search visibility for UK dentists.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Who We Help', href: '/who-we-help/' },
      { label: 'Dentists' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">By Profession</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Search Visibility for Dentists</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">When a patient asks ChatGPT "best dentist near me," AI platforms build their answer from dozens of sources – not just Google. Your Google Business Profile, NHS listings, dental directory entries, review platforms, and website all contribute to whether you get recommended.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Dental practices that appear in AI answers typically have one thing in common: consistent information across every platform. Same practice name, same services listed, same address, same description. AI interprets this consistency as trustworthiness.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What AI Checks for Dental Practices</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">GDC registration</span> – AI cross-references professional body registration as an institutional trust signal</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Review consistency</span> – Google Reviews, Trustpilot, NHS feedback – AI looks for consistent patient experience across platforms</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Service clarity</span> – does your website clearly state what treatments you offer? Vague descriptions create uncertainty</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Local signals</span> – address consistency, map presence, local directory listings all strengthen geographic relevance</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/who-we-help/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Sectors</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/research/uk-ai-visibility-stats/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">UK AI Statistics</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Find out if AI recommends your practice</h2>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
